article_id:624,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding a Log-In Issue [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue where players attempting to log in to the game between <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1563859800"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1563860580"></span> received a &quot;Failed to connect to the server&quot; error message which prevented them from logging in.</div><div><br></div><div>This issue has now been resolved.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1564129800"></span></strong></span></div><div>We have finished investigating this issue.</div><div><br></div><div>Heavy server load caused players to be unable to log in to the game while this issue was occurring.</div><div>This issue has been resolved.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1563862800,update_time1564129745